text: Deportivo La Coruña is a football club which plays in A Coruña, Galicia, Spain. Their current manager is Imanol Idiakez. Their current president is Álvaro García Diéguez. == History == They have won La Liga once, which was in the 1999-2000 season. == League title == * La Liga : 1 ** 1999/00 == League position == Season League Position 2000/01 La Liga 2nd 2001/02 La Liga 2nd 2002/03 La Liga 3rd 2003/04 La Liga 3rd 2004/05 La Liga 8th 2005/06 La Liga 8th 2006/07 La Liga 13th 2007/08 La Liga 9th 2008/09 La Liga 7th === Former position === == References == Category:1906 establishments in Europe Category:1900s establishments in Spain Category:Spanish football clubs Category:Province of A Coruña
